rows.label: qst202806_0010
rows.name: Meh-me-meh...

rows.label: qst202806_0020
rows.name: Meh-eh, me-me-me-mehh...

rows.label: qst202806_0030
rows.name: ...Well?

rows.label: qst202806_0040
rows.name: [ML:undisp]......

rows.label: qst202806_0050
rows.name:
Job is good one!
This unlike any mineral me ever saw.

rows.label: qst202806_0060
rows.name:
For sure?
For really sure?!

rows.label: qst202806_0070
rows.name:
For really sure, meh!
It definitely never-before-seen mineral!

rows.label: qst202806_0080
rows.name: Nice one, Menou.

rows.label: qst202806_0090
rows.name: Good to know all that courage wasn't wasted.

rows.label: qst202806_0100
rows.name: Aww, thanks you guys!

rows.label: qst202806_0110
rows.name:
...All right, to victor go spoils.
Discoverer of mineral have naming rights!

rows.label: qst202806_0120
rows.name: What friend want to call it?

rows.label: qst202806_0130
rows.name: Ahh, um...

rows.label: qst202806_0140
rows.name: Go on, then.

rows.label: qst202806_0150
rows.name: I bet you've got one ready.

rows.label: qst202806_0160
rows.name:
OK. Then how about...
Repymynidro-pom√≤brizepan?

rows.label: qst202806_0170
rows.name: Repymy...what?

rows.label: qst202806_0180
rows.name: I just took the first syllables of all your names...

rows.label: qst202806_0190
rows.name: I've forgotten already!

rows.label: qst202806_0200
rows.name: And is friend not forgetting someone...?

rows.label: qst202806_0210
rows.name: Just call it agate, you doofus.

rows.label: qst202806_0220
rows.name: Seconded.

rows.label: qst202806_0230
rows.name:
Just my name? That's so presumptuous!
I couldn't have done it without you all...

rows.label: qst202806_0240
rows.name: Don't be silly!

rows.label: qst202806_0250
rows.name:
Right, right. Give mineral name of discoverer
is very common thing.

rows.label: qst202806_0260
rows.name: Become proof that friend make this great discovery.

rows.label: qst202806_0270
rows.name: Blades lose their memories eventually...

rows.label: qst202806_0280
rows.name: If that happens to you, Menou,

rows.label: qst202806_0290
rows.name:
at least you'll know the people of Alst
will always remember your name.

rows.label: qst202806_0300
rows.name: That's not so bad, is it?

rows.label: qst202806_0310
rows.name: Hm...

rows.label: qst202806_0320
rows.name: So...I can actually call it "agate"?

rows.label: qst202806_0330
rows.name: Yeah, I think it sounds great.

rows.label: qst202806_0340
rows.name: A pretty name for a pretty chunk of rock.

rows.label: qst202806_0350
rows.name:
Then from this day on, this mineral
known as agate!

rows.label: qst202806_0360
rows.name: Thank you so much!
